* BMAP error handling: an invalid operation mnemonic (ZORCHQ) is flagged.  bmap
* exits nonzero and records severity 4 in the object's HEAD record -- the object
* is still written (the CP-6 model: the linker sees the severity).  Checked
* behaviorally by run_tests.sh, not by a byte-for-byte fixture.
       OUNAME ERRTST
       ZORCHQ 1
       LDA    0
       END
